title: Солёный поцелуй
overview: The main characters, Yulia and Herman, are deeply in love and believe that nothing can tear them apart, especially since Yulia is expecting a child. But one careless mistake leads to tragedy—Herman ends up behind bars. In an instant, their future is shattered, and Yulia must fight alone for herself and her baby. Will they have the strength to endure the trials and keep their love alive?
